node.text:
Happy Tuesday with this glimpse of amazing @villalaCassinella , from the gorgeous gallery of our friend @alexpreview 
Remember that this villa is located between @villa_balbiano  and @villadelbalbianello , and it is accessible only by boat. 

And don’t forget that this villa is NOT owned by Richard Branson, no matter what anyone tells you. 
Wishing everyone a great day!
